snippet.title: Battling a bountry huntress, chaos dwarfs handgunners, and a baby dragon
snippet.description: 60 seconds of gameplay of roguelike Dungeon Mercenary (https://www.schplaf.org/hgames/) of the spring 2018 release. This video shows a lot of new monsters: ghouls, a bounty huntress, chaos dwarfs handgunners. The rogue will survive, but he depleted a lot of consumables...
